{"tid":2460851,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"舒華一早返台「顯眼防疫配備」登韓熱門！　大聲叮嚀粉絲：快回家","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:45:31.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf121e3b9d5f55fd33099afd122271d347181ac","tid":2460851,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:45:31.000Z","msg":"韓團(G)I-DLE成員舒華25日一早現身南韓仁川機場，準備搭機返回台灣，而她的防疫時尚配備成了眾人焦點，韓媒曝光相關新聞後登上熱門新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5525/d5525737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5525%2Fd5525737.jpg&h=694e91b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲舒華戴防疫配備現身機場新聞登上熱門新聞。（圖／翻攝自nate）<br />\n<br />\n舒華25日一早現身仁川機場，灰色針織衫配上綠格紋長裙，很有鄰家女孩的風格，手上還有3個時尚髮帶，其中更令人矚目的是她除了戴上口罩防疫，還特別戴了護目鏡做好萬全準備。韓媒《TVREPORT》以「舒華，戴著防疫護目鏡地偶像」為題發出報導後，竟當上了nate熱門新聞第11名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExR-6dTVoAEL6hp?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExR-6dTVoAEL6hp%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=52e09d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExR-6dSUUAQBKxj?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExR-6dSUUAQBKxj%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=4a87f6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExR-6dSUYAABp5W?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExR-6dSUYAABp5W%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=58af82b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ExR-6dSVgAARLaN?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FExR-6dSVgAARLaN%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=ac1ba777&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲舒華全副武裝準備回台。（圖／取自推特heartflipped_，如遭刪除請見諒）<br />\n<br />\n事實上，舒華看見媒體和粉絲來送行，一路上都笑著揮手打招呼，時不時還送出手指愛心和比著大愛心，要進到CHECK IN區塊時還對大家先鞠躬示意，準備出境時特別大聲說：「我要走了～（大家）快點回家喔！」對幫忙推行李和送行的工作人員與警衛也都親切點頭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1374882009068146692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1374882009068146692&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=edfce5be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1374882009068146692&h=6035df94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1374882009068146692</a>"}]}